Package energy.usef.agr.model

Model classes of the Aggregator.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommonReferenceOperator
    Entity for the COMMON_REFERENCE_OPERATOR table.
    ConnectionForecastSnapshot
    Object used to save a Connection Forecast Snapshot (power per connection per PTU per period).
    ConnectionGroupPowerContainer
    Extension of PowerContainer to link it with a ConnectionGroup
    ConnectionPowerContainer
    Extension of PowerContainer to link it with a Connection
    DeviceMessage
    Entity class representing an ADS Device Message.
    DeviceRequest
    Abstract class for DeviceRequest, with the core information
    Element
    Base entity for the Element Data store.
    ElementDtuData
    A extra object to represent the ElementData per DTU.
    ForecastPowerData
    Extended PowerData for Forecast data.
    IncreaseRequest
    Class representing a Power Increase request (production or consumption), child of VariationRequest.
    InterruptRequest
    Class representing an Interrupt Request for a device.
    PowerContainer
    This object represents all power data within usef.
    PowerData
    Helper object which contains all the fields for one set of PowerData.
    ReduceRequest
    Class representing a Power Reduction request (production or consumption), child of VariationRequest.
    ReportRequest
    Class representing a Report Request for a device.
    ShiftRequest
    Class representing a Shift Request for a device.
    SynchronisationConnection
    Entity for the SYNCHRONISATION_CONNECTION Table.
    SynchronisationConnectionStatus
    Entity for the SYNCHRONISATION_CONNECTION_STATUS Table.
    Udi
    Udi entity class represents the UDI device which forecasts have been received.
    UdiEvent
    Entity class representing a UDI Event.
    UdiPowerContainer
    Extension of PowerContainer to link it with a Connection
    VariationRequest
    Abstract class child of DeviceRequest.
